        "from google.colab import drive\n",
        "drive.mount('/content/drive')\n",
        "import pandas as pd\n",
        "import numpy as np\n",
        "\n",
        "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
        "import seaborn as sns\n",
        "\n",
        "from sklearn.model_selection import train_test_split\n",
        "from sklearn.preprocessing import StandardScaler, LabelEncoder\n",
        "from sklearn.linear_model import LogisticRegression\n",
        "from sklearn.metrics import (\n",
        "    accuracy_score,\n",
        "    precision_score,\n",
        "    recall_score,\n",
        "    f1_score,\n",
        "    roc_auc_score,\n",
        "    confusion_matrix,\n",
        "    roc_curve\n",
        ")\n",
        "\n",
        "import warnings\n",
        "warnings.filterwarnings(\"ignore\")\n",
        "\n",
        "file_path = \"/content/drive/MyDrive/AI_PROJECT/Synthetic Multispectral Crops Data.xlsx\"\n",
        "\n",
        "df = pd.read_excel(file_path)\n",
        "df.head()\n",
        "print(\"Dataset shape:\", df.shape)\n",
        "print(\"\\nColumns:\\n\", df.columns)\n",
        "df.info()\n",
        "df['crop_health_label'].value_counts()\n",
        "target = 'crop_health_label'\n",
        "spatial_cols = ['grid_x', 'grid_y']\n",
        "\n",
        "X = df.drop(columns=[target] + spatial_cols)\n",
        "y = df[target]\n",
        "\n",
        "print(\"Training features:\", X.columns.tolist())\n",
        "print(\"Target column:\", target)\n",
        "encoder = LabelEncoder()\n",
        "y_encoded = encoder.fit_transform(y)\n",
        "\n",
        "print(\"Encoded classes:\", encoder.classes_)\n",
        "X_train, X_test, y_train, y_test = train_test_split(\n",
        "    X,\n",
        "    y_encoded,\n",
        "    test_size=0.2,\n",
        "    random_state=42,\n",
        "    stratify=y_encoded\n",
        ")\n",
        "\n",
        "print(\"Training samples:\", X_train.shape[0])\n",
        "print(\"Testing samples:\", X_test.shape[0])\n",
        "scaler = StandardScaler()\n",
        "\n",
        "X_train_scaled = scaler.fit_transform(X_train)\n",
        "X_test_scaled = scaler.transform(X_test)\n",
        "\n",
        "model = LogisticRegression(max_iter=1000)\n",
        "model.fit(X_train_scaled, y_train)\n",
        "y_pred = model.predict(X_test_scaled)\n",
        "y_prob = model.predict_proba(X_test_scaled)[:, 1]\n",
        "\n",
        "print(\"Accuracy :\", accuracy_score(y_test, y_pred))\n",
        "print(\"Precision:\", precision_score(y_test, y_pred))\n",
        "print(\"Recall   :\", recall_score(y_test, y_pred))\n",
        "print(\"F1 Score :\", f1_score(y_test, y_pred))\n",
        "print(\"ROC AUC  :\", roc_auc_score(y_test, y_prob))\n",
        "cm = confusion_matrix(y_test, y_pred)\n",
        "\n",
        "sns.heatmap(cm, annot=True, fmt='d', cmap='Blues',\n",
        "            xticklabels=encoder.classes_,\n",
        "            yticklabels=encoder.classes_)\n",
        "\n",
        "plt.xlabel(\"Predicted\")\n",
        "plt.ylabel(\"Actual\")\n",
        "plt.title(\"Logistic Regression – Confusion Matrix\")\n",
        "plt.show()\n",
        "fpr, tpr, _ = roc_curve(y_test, y_prob)\n",
        "\n",
        "plt.plot(fpr, tpr, label=f\"AUC = {roc_auc_score(y_test, y_prob):.2f}\")\n",
        "plt.plot([0, 1], [0, 1], linestyle='--')\n",
        "plt.xlabel(\"False Positive Rate\")\n",
        "plt.ylabel(\"True Positive Rate\")\n",
        "plt.title(\"ROC Curve\")\n",
        "plt.legend()\n",
        "plt.show()\n",
        "df['stress_prediction'] = encoder.inverse_transform(\n",
        "    model.predict(scaler.transform(X))\n",
        ")\n",
        "\n",
        "heatmap_data = df.pivot_table(\n",
        "    values='stress_prediction',\n",
        "    index='grid_y',\n",
        "    columns='grid_x',\n",
        "    aggfunc=lambda x: (x == 'Stressed').mean()\n",
        ")\n",
        "\n",
        "plt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))\n",
        "sns.heatmap(heatmap_data, cmap='Reds')\n",
        "plt.title(\"Crop Stress Spatial Heatmap\")\n",
        "plt.xlabel(\"Grid X\")\n",
        "plt.ylabel(\"Grid Y\")\n",
        "plt.show()\n",
        "from sklearn.ensemble import RandomForestClassifier\n",
        "\n",
        "rf_model = RandomForestClassifier(\n",
        "    n_estimators=200,\n",
        "    random_state=42,\n",
        "    class_weight='balanced'\n",
        ")\n",
        "\n",
        "rf_model.fit(X_train, y_train)\n",
        "\n",
        "rf_pred = rf_model.predict(X_test)\n",
        "rf_prob = rf_model.predict_proba(X_test)[:, 1]\n",
        "cm_rf = confusion_matrix(y_test, rf_pred)\n",
        "\n",
        "sns.heatmap(cm_rf, annot=True, fmt='d', cmap='Greens',\n",
        "            xticklabels=encoder.classes_,\n",
        "            yticklabels=encoder.classes_)\n",
        "\n",
        "plt.title(\"Random Forest – Confusion Matrix\")\n",
        "plt.show()\n",
        "comparison = pd.DataFrame({\n",
        "    'Model': ['Logistic Regression', 'Random Forest'],\n",
        "    'Accuracy': [\n",
        "        accuracy_score(y_test, y_pred),\n",
        "        accuracy_score(y_test, rf_pred)\n",
        "    ],\n",
        "    'Precision': [\n",
        "        precision_score(y_test, y_pred),\n",
        "        precision_score(y_test, rf_pred)\n",
        "    ],\n",
        "    'Recall': [\n",
        "        recall_score(y_test, y_pred),\n",
        "        recall_score(y_test, rf_pred)\n",
        "    ],\n",
        "    'F1 Score': [\n",
        "        f1_score(y_test, y_pred),\n",
        "        f1_score(y_test, rf_pred)\n",
        "    ],\n",
        "    'ROC AUC': [\n",
        "        roc_auc_score(y_test, y_prob),\n",
        "        roc_auc_score(y_test, rf_prob)\n",
        "    ]\n",
        "})\n",
        "\n",
        "comparison\n"
